  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-04-22",
    "date": "2021-09-27T01:52:08Z",
    "text": "Climate-Resilient International Development Optimization Act \n\nThis bill directs agencies with direct international development programs and investments to incorporate climate resilience considerations into agency decision making. Agencies that participate in a multilateral entity must encourage the entity to incorporate climate-related risks into the decisions of the entity. The bill also establishes the Working Group on Climate-Resilient International Development in the Department of the Treasury to support such efforts."
  },
